p.k: Finn and Jake challenge a giant monster to a fight but they end up fighting each other. / Princess Bubblegum and Lady Rainicorn go on a quest to find Finn and Jake. / A Race of frog people employ Finn and Jake to help them deal with Prince Huge. / Creepy sleep-peeping Lemongrab upsets Princess Bubblegum. / Clones of Gunter cause chaos in Ooo.
